  "detailed_description": "You are a tester at a high-tech company, responsible for testing a newly developed accelerator designed specifically for wheelchairs!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/284cea565f19bc976fab6585cc7dfd52.poster.avif?t=1694927801\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/284cea565f19bc976fab6585cc7dfd52.webm?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/284cea565f19bc976fab6585cc7dfd52.mp4?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This accelerator has been modified from a jet engine and can unleash a maximum power of 10,000 horsepower. Additionally, it utilizes hydrogen gas as its energy source, so you don't need to worry about environmental concerns.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/448f03ac9f4c3ec1ed82384d4f5c7aa2.poster.avif?t=1694927801\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/448f03ac9f4c3ec1ed82384d4f5c7aa2.webm?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/448f03ac9f4c3ec1ed82384d4f5c7aa2.mp4?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>While this accelerator boasts exceptional performance, it might still have some limitations when facing various real-world scenarios. Your task is to operate this wheelchair equipped with the accelerator, subjecting it to tests in different everyday environments. Your goal is to prove that it's a mature product, ensuring its eventual mass production.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/ebcee66d0f2eaf050aef40d7dbc1fd6d.poster.avif?t=1694927801\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/ebcee66d0f2eaf050aef40d7dbc1fd6d.webm?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566130/extras/ebcee66d0f2eaf050aef40d7dbc1fd6d.mp4?t=1694927801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
